==English==
===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb|enlist|enlists|enlisted|enlisting}}

#To join a [[cause]] or [[organization]], especially [[military]] service.
#:''The army wants potential soldiers to '''enlist'''.''

===Transitive verb===
{{en-verb|enlist|enlists|enlisted|enlisting}}

